    "summary": "We have started Summ( )n to assist teams in navigating the complexities of the world, to support their future innovations and to foster the development of novel concepts and ideas.\n\nWe increasingly witness that the pursuit of these groundbreaking innovations is futile if the teams striving for them are unwilling to evolve and adapt themselves. The teams that don't want to reevaluate their established practices, to scrutinize their underlying assumptions, and to reassess the values that motivate them... well, they fail. And no, they don't fail better. \n\nConsequently, we are increasingly busy with facilitating the transformation of these teams themselves, guiding their journeys of self-discovery and aiding them in becoming a bit less unprepared for the challenges that lie ahead.\n\ntl;dr We keep summoning your futures, together with you.",
